    "es_seo_content": {
      "type": "es-seo-content",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Discover Authentic Arabian Perfumes & Luxury Fragrances in the UK",
        "col1_heading": "Luxury Perfumes for Men & Women",
        "col1_text": "<p>Eterna Scents offers an exceptional range of luxury perfumes for men and women, sourced directly from the world's finest Arabian fragrance houses. From powerful oud-forward masculines to delicate floral feminines, our collection spans every mood and occasion.</p><p>Whether you're searching for a signature daily scent or a statement fragrance for special events, our curated selection ensures you'll find the perfect match — all 100% authentic and long-lasting.</p>",
        "col2_heading": "Gift Perfumes & Special Occasions",
        "col2_text": "<p>Looking for the perfect gift? Our luxury perfume gift sets are beautifully packaged and ready to delight. Arabian fragrances make timeless, sophisticated gifts for birthdays, anniversaries, Eid, weddings and corporate occasions.</p><p>Every Eterna Scents order arrives with complimentary gift-ready packaging, making your purchase look as premium as it smells. A free fragrance sample is included with every full-bottle purchase.</p>",
        "col3_heading": "Oud, Rose & Amber — The Heart of Arabian Perfumery",
        "col3_text": "<p>Arabian perfumery is built on three legendary pillars: oud (agarwood), rose and amber. Oud — sometimes called 'liquid gold' — is one of the rarest and most precious fragrance ingredients in the world, prized for its deep, woody, smoky character.</p><p>At Eterna Scents, we stock authentic oud perfumes from Lattafa, Rasasi, Swiss Arabian and Ahmed Al Maghribi — all at accessible prices with fast UK delivery.</p>",
        "bg_color": "#fdf8f0",
        "navy_color": "#071321",
        "gold_color": "#C9A646"
      }
    }
